These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
City: london, nizza, hannover
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, tiparillo, bluemaster
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, snake
House: tower, futuristic, palace
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, backgammon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, horror, documentary
 1. the person watching western movies is the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person watching documentary movies is the palace house##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is between the person playing backgammon and the person traveling to nizza##2
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 5. the futuristic house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the snake is the person playing whist##1
 7. the owner of the snake is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the futuristic house##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| City      | nizza    | hannover   | london           |
| Cigar          | tiparillo       | bluemaster    | dunhill         |
| Pet         | goat    | snake  | goldfish        |
| House           | tower | futuristic   | palace      |
| Transport   | bike        | subway    | airplane       |
| Game   | snooker     | whist  | backgammon       |
| Movie-Genre         | western     | horror | documentary |

