The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower, zinnia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, vegafina, ritmeester
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bus, motorbike
House: art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, turquise, azure
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, musician
 1. the person who likes azure is the ranch-style house##1
 2. the person who likes azure is the ritmeester-smoker##1
 3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 4. the analyst is between the person playing go and the person playing snooker##2
 5. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing go is the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the musician##1
 8. the person who growsdaffodil is the baccarat-smoker##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Game      | snooker   | monopoly    | go         |
| Flower          | daffodil    | balloon-flower | zinnia          |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | ritmeester  | vegafina     |
| Transport   | motorbike       | bus      | trike         |
