The people have 3 different jobs:  writer, paramedic, architect
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, begonia, daisy
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, whist
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, purple
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, june, february
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, dubstep, punk
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is in the middle##1
 2. the wooden house is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing whist is on the right of the writer##1
 4. the architect is the person who growsbegonia##1
 5. the fan pop is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 7. the fan punk is between the art-deco house and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is the fan pop##1
10. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
11. the fan pop is the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| House      | art-deco | wooden      | cottage      |
| Job         | writer     | paramedic     | architect  |
| Flower   | daisy | amaryllis  | begonia |
| Game   | bridge  | whist     | mah-jongg |
| Color           | brown        | purple | ebony     |
| Birthday         | january    | february | june   |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep        | punk        | pop   |

