2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the italian##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the fonseca-smoker and the polish##2
5. the owner of the fish is between the japanese and the fan classical##2
6. the fan electronic is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the italian##1

